        <div class="text-center">
          <h1 class="lux-hero-title">
            Accelerate your video content strategy with a text‑to‑video approach
          </h1>
          <p class="lux-hero-subtitle mx-auto mt-4">
            I convert existing technical content into self-contained videos that
            drive engagement across your documentation, marketing site, and
            YouTube.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10 sm:mt-12 lg:mt-16">
          <p class="text-center mb-5 lux-kicker text-base">Sample videos</p>
          <div class="mb-5">
            <div class="sm:hidden">
              <label for="sample-video-tabs" class="sr-only">
                Select a sample video category
              </label>
